paragraphs.text:
%md
## Neo4j Streams Sink Cypher Configuration for NYC Taxi and Limousine Commission Data

```
NEO4J_streams_sink_topic_cypher_NYC01: "
    MERGE (r:TaxiRide{ride: event.TripID})
    MERGE (puz:PUZone{zone: event.PUZone})
    MERGE (doz:DOZone{zone: event.DOZone})
    MERGE (puz)-[:IS_PICKUP_ZONE_FOR]->(r)
    MERGE (doz)-[:IS_DROPOFF_ZONE_FOR]->(r)
    MERGE (r)-[:HAS_PICKUP_ZONE]->(puz)
    MERGE (r)-[:HAS_DROPOFF_ZONE]->(doz)"
```

paragraphs.title: NYC Filter the Dataframe and replace the old one
paragraphs.text:
%sql
CREATE OR REPLACE TEMP VIEW NYC_OPEN_DATA AS
SELECT 
    CONCAT(PULocationID, "-", DOLocationID) AS TripID,
    passenger_count,
    trip_distance,
    PULocationID,
    PUBorough,
    PUZone,
    DOLocationID,
    DOBorough,
    DOZone,
    total_amount
FROM NYC_OPEN_DATA
WHERE PULocationID <> '-'
AND DOLocationID <> '-'
AND PULocationID <> DOLocationID

paragraphs.title: NYC Create a new Dataframe that will be used to send the data to Kafka
paragraphs.text:
%sql
CREATE OR REPLACE TEMP VIEW NYC_OPEN_DATA_KAFKA_STAGE AS
SELECT 
    TripID AS KEY,
    TO_JSON(
        STRUCT(
            TripID,
            passenger_count,
            trip_distance,
            PULocationID,
            PUBorough,
            PUZone,
            DOLocationID,
            DOBorough,
            DOZone,
            total_amount
        )
    ) AS VALUE
FROM NYC_OPEN_DATA
